title: Recap: Tech drops a pair of games in Clearwater - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Recap: Tech drops a pair of games in Clearwater - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: CLEARWATER, Fla. – Texas Tech softball (3-5) battled in a pair of games on Friday but came up short against Northwestern (5-1) and #24 UCF (5-3) on day two of the St. Pete/Clearwater Elite Invitational.
